ile/TCHM/110%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c575%2c20210804%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,110,上訴,575,20210804,2","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"575","JDATE":"20210804","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}